978-1734314509 : Bad check-digit 9; should be 2
978-1788399081 : Good
978-1788399083 : Bad check-digit 3; should be 1
978-2-74839-908-0 : Good
978-2-74839-908-5 : Bad check-digit 5; should be 0</pre>
